INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1387,1,'2022-06-23 19:29:12','2022-06-23 19:29:12','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"3463\">How long have you been programming in Kotlin? If you think you know all the features available in Kotlin, well, think again. Here are 5 features you may not have known that existed in Kotlin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 id=\"0881\">Destructuring</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"84fc\">Some people think that destructing only works in some languages like JavaScript and Python. But this feature is available in Kotlin as well.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"234c\">You can replace all the instances of long data types with one word that better describes your code.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 id=\"5ece\">Backticks</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"2ef7\">Do you need to write a specific variable name but that’s a hard keyword in Kotlin? In most languages, they <strong>forbid </strong>you to do it; but not Kotlin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 id=\"4a94\">Conclusion</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"c510\">Kotlin will never fail to surprise you. It is an ever-growing programming language which is a perfect mix of every feature you want and need. The language already has such a great leap; more updates in the future will only make it better.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','5 Untold Features of Kotlin','Hidden features of Kotlin — How long have you been programming in Kotlin? If you think you know all the features available in Kotlin, well, think again. Here are 5 features you may not have known that existed in Kotlin','inherit','closed','closed','','1385-revision-v1','','','2022-06-23 19:29:12','2022-06-23 19:29:12','',1385,'http://softsolutions.local/?p=1387',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1388,1,'2022-06-23 19:32:53','2022-06-23 19:32:53','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"e56c\">Closures are one of the core concepts in functional programming, and it is must-have knowledge for every JavaScript developer. Here I have prepared 10 closure challenges, many of which are frequently asked in interviews.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"bc4e\">Are you ready, challenger? Enjoy this journey!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"b35e\">Each challenge is a code snippet, and you need to say what the output of this code will be.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 id=\"0fe0\">1. Scope</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"fc35\">Before talking about closures, we must understand the concept of scope, which is the cornerstone of understanding closures.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"f6b4\">What is the output of this code snippet?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"3257\">It is very simple. I believe that all challengers know that the output result is&nbsp;<code>10</code>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>By default, there is a global scope.</li><li>A local scope is created by a function or a code block.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When <code>console.log(a)</code> is executed, the JavaScript engine will first look for <code>a</code> in the local scope created by the function <code>foo</code>. When the JavaScript engine can’t find <code>a</code>, it will try to find <code>a</code> in its outer scope, which is the global scope. Then it turns out that the value of <code>a</code> is 10.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','10 JavaScript Closure Challenges Explained With Diagrams','Closures are one of the core concepts in functional programming, and it is must-have knowledge for every JavaScript developer. Here I have prepared 10 closure challenges, many of which are frequently asked in interviews','publish','open','open','','10-javascript-closure-challenges-explained-with-diagrams','','','2022-06-23 19:40:52','2022-06-23 19:40:52','',0,'http://softsolutions.local/?p=1388',0,'post','',0);
